547
00:37:00,430 --> 00:37:01,350
Nananatiling nalulumbay

548
00:37:01,350 --> 00:37:02,190
hindi malulutas ang anuman.

549
00:37:02,910 --> 00:37:03,830
Ngayon makikita ko ang bola

550
00:37:03,830 --> 00:37:04,790
