551
00:37:05,060 --> 00:37:07,660
Ilalabas ko ang sama ng loob ko sa court.

552
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:11,700
Kaya, lalaruin ko ang buong laban.

553
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:14,100
Mga ginoo, walang matigas na damdamin.

554
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:15,990
- Buong tugma?
- Puno?

555
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:17,620
Tanging sina Meng Wan at Qingsheng

556
00:37:17,620 --> 00:37:18,460
