557
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:20,020
Bumubuo ka ng sarili mong mga koponan.

558
00:37:20,750 --> 00:37:22,140
Hindi ba pwedeng i-corner at huminto

559
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:22,980
