560
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:24,990
- Ayos.
- Sige.

561
00:37:24,990 --> 00:37:25,870
Iyan ay magiging perpekto.

562
00:37:25,870 --> 00:37:27,010
- Oo.
- Sige.

563
00:37:41,290 --> 00:37:42,140
